This article highlights the support and praise that Judge Brett Kavanaugh has received from various groups, including his female law clerks, state attorneys general, and members of the Yale University community. The female law clerks commend him for his support and mentorship of women lawyers, as well as his achievement of gender parity in hiring. The state attorneys general describe him as an outstanding jurist committed to upholding the Constitution and the rule of law. The Yale community recognizes him as a faithful servant to his community and one of the nation's most distinguished jurists.